&lt;br&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
投影片連結: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.slideshare.net/mobile/simonbelak/doing-data-science-with-clojure-65886938&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;線上看&lt;/a&gt;
